					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1922529&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203728" alt="Agent MacLeod" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1922529)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-macleod" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1922529); return false;" >Agent MacLeod</a></span> <span class="odate time_1416988778 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">26 Nov 2014 07:59</span>
