<p>I hate to be the minority here, but I don't even quite understand the story. Is the implication that the Foundation destroyed the universe and then made it look like nothing had changed? Novoting until someone explains the story. I'm sorry I'm don't understand, when this is clearly both the result of a lot of effort and very popular.</p>

